Modular sofas

Modular fabric sofas
Sofa modules
Modular coated fabric sofas

Sofas That Bring Out Your Creative Side


No one does flexible furniture better than us. Our modular sofas, in multiple styles, colours, and materials are proof of this. Add or subtract footstools, backrests, armrests, and design the sofa you’ve always dreamed of. The GRÖNLID lets you add sofa modules to keep up with your growing needs while the comfortable LANDSKRONA and SÖDERHAMN allow you to create the perfect sofa set for yourself by adding chaise lounges and storage modules. We’ve even got something for smaller spaces - our VALLENTUNA series goes form sofa unit to a single bed if you need space for your guest to sleep.
